body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, I'm Harold Young from SafeCar Solutions. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Judy. Can you please provide me with your date of birth?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's the third of May, nineteen eighty-five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Judy. Could you also tell me the last four digits of your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, they are double four, triple five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for sharing the information, Judy. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, I am happy with the service so far.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I'm glad to hear that, Judy. Thank you for your time. Have a great day!
